{"tid":617211,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港食飯已經貴過日本好耐","createTime":"2018-04-04T19:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T01:30:14.000Z","uid":88235,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b8f90ca9280b5bd74102842b854a35d1f94c7aee","tid":617211,"uid":88235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T19:28:11.000Z","msg":"就咁講普通連鎖餐廳<br />\n唔好講咩吉野家 一定係日本平<br />\n王將餃子6隻先十幾蚊 香港八方x集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/05/032432_6480a7e5205e39ee4537ea42b0b34259.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F05%2F032432_6480a7e5205e39ee4537ea42b0b34259.png&h=9fc37b6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n普通快餐店有牛有雞有蝦 白飯任食咁樣先60蚊<br />\n再望下大x樂 大快x 真係狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d6ca4ef8a161b5fa30ee48c8425cd835cba314","tid":617211,"uid":88235,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T19:38:41.000Z","msg":"邊個負評我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e682d8f27f6fe8e175382549b880572c7c2dc49","tid":617211,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T19:41:52.000Z","msg":"冇辦法啦，香港咩都靠入口，舖租又畀人炒貴晒<br />\n人地日本食物都係本土嘢，舖租又冇香港咁癲<br />\n最低工資又高過你，食材又好過你平過你，香港人真係慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65060c77bf687d7e7ae60d3aefa4e5f54ac1e94","tid":617211,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T00:32:15.000Z","msg":"等睇人入黎罵你食輻射野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80767e35dbf2ca1ad9c5b1dc7e0d834bdae79acd","tid":617211,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T00:50:11.000Z","msg":"去日本食幾貴都覺得抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13fb6e